  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201405/2cbc7327dd584ccdb3b5fedc7d3a4e96.jpg\" /></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<p>\n\t\t<a href=\"http://www.cctalk.com/gongkaike/151369517/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Public Speaking ：如何成就一场出色英语演讲</strong></a><span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong><a href=\"http://www.cctalk.com/gongkaike/151120442/\"><br />\n\t\t</a></strong><span style=\"color: #006400;\">时间：5月28日（星期三）20:00 - 21:00</span><br />\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #006400;\">主讲老师：Victor</span></span><span style=\"color: #000;\"><span style=\"color: #006400;\">（<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/wordoor/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击关注老师的沪江部落&gt;&gt;&gt;</a>）</span><br />\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #006400;\">公开课地点：英语大厅（<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击下载CCTalk</a>）</span></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<a href=\"http://www.cctalk.com/gongkaike/151369517/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/f149ba0b08bd4f7d85f0034ae5a68a94.png\" /></a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">（本公开课只有注册用户才能参与，花<span style=\"color: #f00;\"><strong>5秒钟</strong></span>完成<strong><a href=\"http://bulo.hjenglish.com/n1/?source=en_gkkyd\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">注册吧&gt;&gt;&gt;</a></strong>）</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t你是否崇拜过在众人面前侃侃而谈，涛涛不绝的大师呢？你又是否在做述职报告或者其他公开会议中总是被抢话而得不到上级赏识呢？如何让其他人听你说话，被你所感染呢？这堂课Wordoor就要给他家带来超级干货：如何成就一场出色的演讲！当然我们的演讲语言是英语，但是这是一场适合所有人群的公开课，通过这堂课让我们都成为&ldquo;自信的演说家&rdquo;。</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #0000cd;\"><strong>这节课，Victor会告诉大家公开演讲的重要性，怎么才能做一个好的演讲，需要注意些什么，怎么加强你演讲的技巧。</strong></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<strong><span style=\"color: #b22222;\">【讲师简介】</span></strong></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<strong><span style=\"color: #000;\">Victor </span></strong></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">Victor is originally from Holland, where he studied New Media and Business Information Systems. After graduation from the University of Amsterdam, he moved to China and now lives in Shanghai where he worked as an event manager and language department manager for Wordoor</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><strong>【公开课大纲】<br />\n\t\t</strong></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">-First thoughts on your presentation</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">-How to prepare for your speech</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">-Practical speaking tips and how to overcome any fears</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">-How to deliver a great speech and what to avoid</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">-What to do after your speech</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201402/d8c8e5c03e5649efa20a6230df0bc72c.jpg\" /></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">本次课程完全免费，您需要做的就是：</span><a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #f00;\"><strong>下载沪江全新语音学习软件--CCtalk&gt;&gt;点击下载</strong></span></a></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201209/58f013100fe44857a846c5c5aef19325.gif\" style=\"width: 377px; height: 15px;\" /></strong></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>请注意！参与本活动须使用沪江全新语音学习软件CCTalk，使用指南如下：</strong></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1.<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bulo.hjenglish.com/n1/?source=eng2009\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">注册</span></a></strong>沪江网获得用户名（已是沪江用户的不必注册）；<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_gkkyd\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/fdac82641c98410a9fb1352dcdff5cd3.jpg\" /></a><br />\n\t\t2. 点击网址<a href=\"http://class.yeshj.com/zt/cctalk\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(7, 93, 179);\">http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk</span></a